<ab facs="#facs_304_r1l18"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> daʒ wır <expan>maynte<ex>n</ex></expan> des Jr ein <expan>genüge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſolt . VVan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_304_r1l19">wır das <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> gemaint <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd auch <expan>awſſ<ex>er</ex>halben</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_304_r1l20">Stat niht geleyts <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / wıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo ſol der <expan>obg<ex>e</ex>n<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> Yoſep Jud . ʒwo </ab>
