<ab facs="#facs_304_r1l22">tag ſchıerıſt vor vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſıcher ſein on geuerd . Wer <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> daʒ </ab>
