<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan>, als ir uns <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Yosep Püczels des juden
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Nu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, daz wir
                            <expan>maynte<ex>n</ex></expan>, des ir ein
                            <expan>genüge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> solt, wan wir das
                            <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan> gemaint
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        auch <expan>awss<ex>er</ex>halben</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat niht geleyts
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so sol
                        der <expan>obg<ex>e</ex>n<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> Yosep jud zwo meyl
                        auszwendig <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>zuwand<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date">sand <expan>Walp<ex>ur</ex>gen</expan> tag schierist</q>01.05.1422</note>
</app> vor uns und den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sicher sein on geverd.
                        Wer <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz sich <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> keinr <expan>geg<ex>en</ex></expan> im
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>handlot</expan>, des wir doch niht
                                <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>, mag uns ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol getrawen, daz uns das niht wol
                        gemaint <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> und darczu tun
                            <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan>, was uns darczu zu tun gebüret, so wir
                        das erfüren <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan>. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
